        "en" => "Sit and adjust your feet according to the designated place and then bend your back forward until you grab bar in wide grip with your palms facing down. Exhale as you pull the bar until your back becomes straight  and the bar reaches the lower of your chest. Inhale while returning it back to the starting position. Repeat.",
