        "en" => "Sit and adjust your feet according to the designated place and then bend your back forward until you grab bar in medium grip with your palms facing up. Exhale as you pull the bar until your back becomes straight and the bar reaches the lower of your chest. Inhale while return it back to the starting position. Repeat.",
